title: Five Nights At Freddy's - The Worst Of Both Worlds?
description: Five Nights At Freddy's has been clearing up at the box office, raking in more than $200 Million against a $20 Million budget. But is it a decent adaptation of the hit game, or a disappointing flop coasting on name recognition?
